    "bio_exists": true,
    "bio_summary": "Jonathon Ng (born 23 December 1995), better known by his stage name EDEN is an Irish electronic music producer and singer-songwriter based in Dublin. He formerly operated as Eden Project, an alias that was discontinued in 2015. Ng's work as Eden Project featured more conventional styles of electronic dance music such as dubstep and drum and bass, while EDEN saw him venturing into a more indie pop style.\n\nNg released over 40 tracks as The Eden Project including 6 EPs, as well as several remixes. ",
